: 718}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Gold\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 734}, {\"ngram\": \"day\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 758}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 806, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Clickhereto buy\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 805}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Biles cut a confident figure before she took to the runway, moments after taking a tumble on the second of two warm-up attempts before the final commenced.\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 963, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 808, \"to\": 813}, {\"ngram\": \"a confident figure\", \"from\": 818, \"to\": 836}, {\"ngram\": \"the runway\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"a tumble\", \"from\": 889, \"to\": 897}, {\"ngram\": \"the second\", \"from\": 901, \"to\": 911}, {\"ngram\": \"two warm-up attempts\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 935}, {\"ngram\": \"the final commenced\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But that did not faze her as she enjoyed a relaxed conversation with USA teammate Jade Carey before doing what she does best on the biggest stage.\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 1111, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1034, \"end\": 1037, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.956091901552439, \"rank\": 0.036246014398223565, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1047, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Jade Carey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jade_Carey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a relaxed conversation\", \"fr