al.\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1659, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial\", \"from\": 1626, \"to\": 1658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her all-around victory, Biles admitted that she could not help but feel threatened by Andrade after she took gold in Tokyo three years ago.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1757, \"end\": 1764, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999999992455741, \"rank\": 7.512154411441674e-10, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}, {\"begin\": 1788, \"end\": 1793, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999989198241942, \"rank\": 1.0746393485381993e-06, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her all-around victory\", \"from\": 1671, \"to\": 1693}, {\"ngram\": \"Biles\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1700}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have never had an athlete that close - it definitely put me on my toes and brought out the best athlete in myself,\\\" said the American.\", \"from\": 1812, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1940, \"end\": 1948, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9993055988917441, \"rank\": 0.0006895144341723786, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1840}, {\"ngram\": \"my toes\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"the best athlete\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1918}]}, {\"sentenc